Text: no offense, but it's 21st century, please don't do 128 kbit, do at least 192 constant bitrate or level 3 variable bitrate :)

Purest Feeling was on a tape reel, and when they were ripped, it had been played a few times. I dont think any higher bitrate would help with audio quality, and most people still wouldn't be able to tell a difference between the reel, and the files here.
